title: War of the Roses: Maybe You Should Date Him
description: Elise noticed that her sister-in-law, Kim, has been dressing much nicer lately and started to style her hair.  Kim cheated on Elise's brother-in-law before they ever got married so now Elise thinks something fishy is going on again and wants to know if her sister-in-law is cheating again.
